STEPS:->
1. sudo apt update
2. sudo apt install docker.io -y
3. sudo usermod -aG docker admin(aws user)
4. docker build -t ___
5. run on aws docker run --privileged -p 5000:5000 scanner

dont forget to add 5000 port to security group ec2
